  "texts": [
    "The fused output is then used to predict an answer via an MLP.Nuthalapati et al. [123] use a dual scene graph approach, using both visual and semantic graphs.",
    "These graphs are merged into a single graph embedding using a novel GAT architecture [102] that is able to attend to edges as well as nodes.",
    "The graphs are enriched with negative entities that appear in the question but not the graph.",
    "Pruning then takes place to remove nodes and edges that are K hops away from features mentioned in the question.",
    "A decoder is then used to produce an answer to the inputted question."
  ],
